# User-generated world models contain sensitive characterizations of real,
# named people — in both the source Markdown and the rendered HTML. Never commit
# them. Each context lives in its own folder (e.g. world_model/ or
# <context>_world_model/) holding the .md sources and the generated .html views.
*world_model*/
*world-model*/

# legacy flat-file layout, and any stray rendered views
*world_model*.md
*world-model*.md
*world_model*.html
*world-model*.html

# but DO keep the skill's own reference files
!references/
!references/**
